{"tid":638452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發現啲肥人跳舞攞左少少自信,但啲言行都好撚煩?","createTime":"2018-04-22T17:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T17:32:12.000Z","uid":176927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12828b63074eba80355d07599a7fdad8d6d1d502","tid":638452,"uid":176927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"以前識落有個肥仔叫SK<br />\n佢講野好撚怪好撚大聲好撚煩<br />\n學左兩三年已經好鐘意比較邊個tutor勁同廢<br />\n甚至好鍾意比較咩舞種難啲<br />\n學popping果陣又話hiphop易啲<br />\n學hiphop果陣又話popping易啲<br />\n又鍾意批評新人<br />\n人地對話又鍾意介入搶野講<br />\n又無啦啦係到跳比人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多肥人舞者(特別唔係好勁果啲)都有啲類似性格<br />\n唔講都知呢啲人未接觸舞蹈之前成係中學比人杯葛,學跳舞之後又自信到過左火<br />\n屌真係好撚煩<br />\n又無啦啦強調自己跳舞輕香啲咩"},{"pid":"88ad741354ed0fa58e47461d1b4388e94cfe9864","tid":638452,"uid":73066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:29:34.000Z","msg":"出黎battle咪得"},{"pid":"d7465db4f8a867bd221784b1505daa32683ead34","tid":638452,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/012944_78344a611c5c51cfcb8a8aa197aa2bb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F012944_78344a611c5c51cfcb8a8aa197aa2bb3.png&h=03716f8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1852d21d19c1e5803e1b5a40ce0ed15065a03f47","tid":638452,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:32:12.000Z","msg":"條裙咁撚靚嘥撚哂"}]}